{"tid":542353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來家庭月入十萬以上只係得6%人咁少？","createTime":"2018-01-27T11:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T07:56:04.000Z","uid":31173,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2e313aaee6136e355fe24d488ba646750cc62181","tid":542353,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"係格黎post見到呢個表<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/192622_22f97a882bf109eb9699424fdd1cf0dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F192622_22f97a882bf109eb9699424fdd1cf0dc.png&h=b1cdb760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來家庭月入十萬以上只係得6%人咁少？ 計晒全屋人wor，講真真係俾預期中少，阿爸阿媽仔女加埋晒，可能講緊每人搵3-4萬已經夠（我知都難，但唔係冇可能，仲要講緊4-50歲呢個年紀）"},{"pid":"8cdc389b1adb727d5e6b7b10abdee899fd220f63","tid":542353,"uid":85819,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a531e0436f0c12ec20932ff0c8dc9c19e9f23baa","tid":542353,"uid":154684,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"咁仔女成家立室都分多兩戶出嚟啦"},{"pid":"5a34be02ad5e75997c6d451973ee0f7f000432e2","tid":542353,"uid":49853,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:33:41.000Z","msg":"on9,年紀大就=搵得多?<br />\n你見唔到大把中年人做侍應，收銀呢d搵得一萬幾千"},{"pid":"c96877f0ac5a8bf7410659d680d584e611f6a0fe","tid":542353,"uid":42188,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"公屋撚: 我識人係上面有幾層樓收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ff0267a46dd663779d558beaabf580e6907d15","tid":542353,"uid":129506,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"其實好撚多人返工係冇報稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f85ca2dacde8ff29ec31e6052961030724de99","tid":542353,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a531e0436f0c12ec20932ff0c